# Hospital Management System
A Hospital Management System developed using Python and SQLite to manage patient records and appointments through a role-based menu driven application.

The project provides separate modules for Admin, Doctor, and Patient roles. 
It allows users to store patient information, search records, update details, manage appointments, and maintain hospital data efficiently using a SQLite database.

## Features
### Patient Management
* Add new patient records
* View all patient records
* Search patient using Patient ID
* Update patient information
* Delete patient records

### Appointment Management

* Book appointments for patients
* View appointment details
* Cancel existing appointments

### Role-Based Access
#### Admin
* Manage patient records
* Manage appointments
* Access all system features

#### Doctor

* View patient records
* Search patient details
* View appointment information

#### Patient

* Book appointments
* View appointments
* Cancel appointments

## Technologies Used

* Python
* SQLite3

## Database Design
### Patients Table
Stores patient information including:

* Patient ID
* Name
* Age
* Disease

### Appointments Table

Stores appointment information including:

* Appointment ID
* Patient ID
* Doctor Name
* Appointment Date
* Appointment Time

The tables are connected using a Foreign Key relationship between Patients and Appointments.

